%F A106732 a(n) = first entry of v(n), where v(n) = M*v(n-1), M is the 2 X 2 matrix {{0, -3}, {1, 5}} and v(0) is the column vector (0, 1).
%F A106732 G.f.: -3*x/(1 - 5*x + 3*x^2).
%F A106732 a(n) = 5*a(n-1) - 3*a(n-2), a(0) = 0, a(1) = -3.
